column5: Well.... Looks like i'm an uncle as of some time early this morning. Still cant believe it myself. I dont really know much of the details either. Healthy baby boy by the name of Noah, that's about all I know. Havent been to the hospital yet. Probably will be sometime tonight. My borthers GF is doing alright by the sounds of things. I'm happy for them and Hopefully all goes well for them.  Now I got a little fishing buddy!  JP
CONGRATS !!! I GOT 2 AND JUST LOVE TO TAKE EM FISHIN.  'THIS IS GONNA BE A CHANGIN DAY IN YOUR LIFE !!!'
thanks guys! I appreciate it.  and mercman, I hope it is a "changin' day"!
congrats man youre a lucky dude
